title: Hansel & Gretel: Witch Hunters
subTitle: Brother-sister duo Hansel and Gretel are professional witch hunters who help innocent villagers. But they soon stumble upon a case that could hold the key to their past.

title: Backtrace
subTitle: A thief suffers from amnesia after committing a bank heist and is imprisoned. Seven years later, he is injected with a drug that restores his memory so that he may recover the stolen money.

title: Escape Plan 2: Hades
subTitle: Security expert Ray Breslin forms a team of skilled personnel after escaping 'The Tomb'. However, when one of his colleagues goes missing, Breslin is forced to revisit the group that imprisoned him.

title: DSC
subTitle: Talented directors provide an entertaining insight into the most intriguing stories and anecdotes concerning some of their best works.

title: Street Kings
subTitle: After his wife's death, Detective Tom Ludlow casts aside all rules and becomes a murder suspect. He begins questioning his colleagues' loyalties and sets out to prove his innocence.

title: Unsane
subTitle: A young woman is involuntarily committed to a mental institution, where she is confronted by her greatest fear. But is it real or a product of her delusion?

subTitle: Katniss Everdeen realises that she is no longer fighting for survival. So, she sets out to assassinate the tyrannical President Snow and liberate the people of Panem.

subTitle: With the help of warrior Rita Vrataski, Major William Cage has to save Earth and the human race from an alien species, after being caught in a time loop.

title: Troy

subTitle: Four magicians who perform on streets steal a tremendous amount of money that belongs to an insurance magnate while they are pursued by police authorities.

subTitle: When terrorists suddenly invade the White House, police officer John Cale springs into action to protect his daughter and the President of the United States.

subTitle: A group of misfits are coerced to work together for a dangerous mission in Corto Maltese. Despite their differences, they learn to trust each other and collaborate as a team.

title: Child's Play
subTitle: Karen buys a high-tech doll named Chucky for her son, Andy, on his birthday. However, horrific events follow as the doll reveals its ominous tendencies.

title: Recoil
subTitle: When his family is killed by a notorious gang, Ryan Varett, a former police officer, suits up to seek revenge against the perpetrators.

subTitle: Cam, a bike messenger, is wanted by the Chinese mafia and he is on the run while learning parkour after crashing into a beautiful woman.

subTitle: Upon getting adopted by the Littles, Stuart, a mouse, is unwelcomed by his new brother George. So, when Stuart begins to feel low the family helps him find his real parents.

title: Creed
subTitle: Adonis Johnson trains with Rocky Balboa, the legendary boxer. Following Rocky's guidance, he works hard to earn recognition in the boxing world.

subTitle: Princess Diana of an all-female Amazonian race rescues US pilot Steve. Upon learning of a war, she ventures into the world of men to stop Ares, the god of war, from destroying mankind.

subTitle: Jack Dwyer and his family move to a country in Southeast Asia. However, a sudden and violent uprising forces them to flee or risk being executed.

subTitle: Rocky trains his friend Apollo Creed for a match against Ivan Drago, an indestructible Russian boxer. However, when Apollo dies in the ring, Rocky vows to avenge his death.

title: Braven
subTitle: A logger and his father head to their hunting cabin, hoping for a quiet weekend. Instead, they find themselves in a kill-or-be-killed stand for survival when they encounter a gang of drug traffickers.

title: Braven

title: Alex Cross
subTitle: While investigating a murder, Alex Cross learns of a ruthless serial killer. However, things soon spiral out of control, leading him on a quest for revenge and uncovering a dark web of conspiracy.

subTitle: After a devastating accident shatters his world, a once-celebrated champion boxer spirals into a destructive abyss. Subsequently, he decides to fight for his daughter and revive his fading career.

subTitle: Katniss volunteers to replace her sister in a tournament that ends only when one participant remains. Pitted against contestants who have trained for this all their life, she has little to rely on.
